{"tid":1001840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日比隻小蝻亞蟲非禮！！！","createTime":"2019-01-30T12:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T13:52:32.000Z","uid":17640,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3128a1bf78e868d84a32640602b2eee8a58b1bb0","tid":1001840,"uid":17640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"今日係尖沙咀比隻大約4,5歲既蝻亞仔摸左下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時因為條街好窄<br />\n所以我見到隻蝻迎面行黎既時候已經側身避開<br />\n點知係我地擦身而過個一刻 <br />\n佢伸手用力摸左我個肚一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個刻我呆左係度反應唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無想像過會比個細路非禮<br />\n當下一秒我回頭望向佢既時候<br />\n佢就用一個得戚既眼神望返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下我就100%肯定佢係特登摸我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個下無捉住佢係因為我估唔到<br />\n佢咁細個就有非禮人既概念<br />\n而且諗住細路仔就由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我返到屋企就後悔啦<br />\n根本呢d係蝻亞人既天性<br />\n好似d蝗蟲貪小便宜一樣 都係天性<br />\n我唔應該放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講咩「他只是個孩子啊！」<br />\n細個係咁 大個都會係咁 甚至更過份<br />\n<br />\n我開post係希望如果其他絲遇到呢個情況<br />\n千奇唔好似我咁啞忍 唔好縱容佢地<br />\n放過佢地一次佢地只會變本加厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf4b62a09b0c1c8d04ec514c32d8daa67583307","tid":1001840,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d364e2bf1936cfe8123a28be4c9b5d7204c0bed","tid":1001840,"uid":210161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"係咪肚腩大過胸<br />\n佢掂到個肚以為自己成功達陣 先咁囂張"},{"pid":"8b7c2345ab3727be7a6d1bd07c22a3ead41cb9c0","ti